          "instruction": "Answer the questions based on the audio.",
          "prompt_html": "<h1>NOTE COMPLETION 13</h1><p><strong>Questions 16 - 20</strong></p><p>Complete the notes.</p><p>Use <strong>NO MORE THAN THREE WORDS AND / OR A NUMBER</strong> for each answer.</p><p><strong>Solaris Hotel and Holiday Village - Activities</strong></p><p>Beaches: main beach + <blank data-qid=\"q16\"/></p><p>beach (17s or over).</p><p>Two lifeguards on duty from 9.00 a.m. to 6.00 p.m. on main beach (none on adult beach).</p><ul><li>Decked area with sun loungers in front of Harvest Restaurant with our 25-metre swimming pool.</li><li>Steps from pool area to beach - wash feet in foot pool to remove sand.</li><li>Fresh-water <blank data-qid=\"q17\"/> on beach and in pool area.</li></ul><p>Sports</p><p>Eight tennis courts and three squash courts.</p><p>Fully equipped gym (no under 18s).</p><p>Various snooker and pool tables located in the <blank data-qid=\"q18\"/> next to the bar.</p><p>Small charge for hiring equipment.</p><p>Water Sports</p><p>Water skiing + jet skis available (extra charge).</p><p>Snorkelling, inflatables and pedallos (free).</p><p>(details from water sports office).</p><p>Library and Cinemas</p><p>Library contains books, magazines + newspapers. See the <blank data-qid=\"q19\"/> for terms + conditions.</p><p>Two cinemas show three different films each every day.</p><p>Shows at 2.00 p.m., 5.30 p.m. and 8.30 p.m (first two shows always have a film for kids).</p><p>Children under <blank data-qid=\"q20\"/> not allowed to attend 8.30 p.m. shows.</p>",
